description.short: Amani Earthy Living is an earthy retreat in Mani with incredible sea views, consisting of two unique villas designed to offer a holistic and luxurious holiday experience.

roomTypes.name: 3 Bedroom Sea View Villa with Private Pool
roomTypes.description:
The 3 Bedroom Sea View Villa with Private Pool, is the luxurious synthesis of The Sea View Maisonette with Sharing Pool and The Sea View Suite with Sharing Pool. Two fine properties, protected in privacy as they are conveniently disconnected and they feature separate entrances, wrap up an exclusive vacation experience that can host up to 9 guests; in the spacious property’s bedrooms and in the living room sofa beds that can host three guests in total, as it conveniently folds out to a second single bed.

The 3 Bedroom Sea View Villa with Private Pool is designed to protect the retreat of its guests who can refuge in the lavish villa hideaways of the indoor and outdoor spaces, enjoying the privilege of undisturbed views towards the sea and the authentic Mani surroundings as well as the signature emerald water pool.

roomTypes.name: Sea View Suite with Sharing Pool
roomTypes.description:
The Sea View Suite with Sharing Pool an ideal getaway for guests that appreciate the proximity to the garden. The soothing ambience of this charming and light-filled suite, blends wonderfully with the breath-taking views of its exterior.

It features a comfortable living room and a fully equipped kitchen with dining room area, designed to offer easy navigation leading to the Suite’s exquisite terrace with the emerald Sharing Pool. The living room’s sofa bed can host two guests, as it conveniently folds out to a second single bed. The spacious bedroom with the double bed, features a flat screen TV and a wide vanity desk, while the calming earthy colored bathroom boasts double sinks and a walk-in shower.

roomTypes.name: 2 Bedroom Sea View Villa with Private Pool
roomTypes.description:
The 2 Bedroom Sea View Villa with Private Pool sets the tone for an impeccable stay that reflects the authentic character of Mani.

The Ground Floor features a living room with a sofa bed by the main entrance, that can host one guest. On the same level and in an open living concept is the fully equipped kitchen and the dining area that leads to the impressive arched private balcony with a build-in sofa and lounge chair. The ground floor also features a W.C.

The property’s 1st floor boasts two elegant -double beds- bedrooms that lead to a shared spacious sea view balcony, as well as a bathroom with a shower.

The impressive outdoor premises feature a shaded outdoor dining area, the signature emerald private pool, sun beds with umbrellas and cozy outdoor lounge areas.

roomTypes.name: Sea View Maisonette with Sharing Pool
roomTypes.description:
The Sea View Maisonette with Sharing Pool welcomes guests to tune in the liberating privacy of a chic and relaxing stay. It offers a comfortable and refined stay, in harmony with the property’s magnificent landscape.

The elevated ground floor with private entrance is cosy and inviting: the living room comes with spectacular views as well as a sofa bed by the main entrance, that can host one guest. On the same level and in an open living concept is the fully equipped kitchen and the dining area that leads to the impressive private balcony with an outdoor dining table and comfortable chairs. The elevated ground floor also features a W.C.

The Maisonette’s 1st floor boasts two elegant -double beds- bedrooms that lead to a shared spacious balcony, offering amazing sea sunset views and relaxing hours of leisure inspired reverie. The 1st floor also features a bathroom with a walk-in shower.

roomTypes.name: Amani Estate
roomTypes.description: The Amani Estate is the synthesis of the 2 Bedroom Sea View Villa with Private Pool and the 3 Bedroom Sea View Villa with Private Pool, offered as one luxurious estate that can host up to 14 guests. A graceful constellation of all the Amani independent properties, with two private outdoor premises with signature pools, outdoor lounges, dining areas and the unique views of the Messinian gulf.

description.short: Head to the desert for stillness, adventure and breath-taking beauty. Anantara Sahara Tozeur Resort & Villas is your luxurious gateway to the majesty of the Sahara.

roomTypes.name: Deluxe Sahara View Suite
roomTypes.description: At 79 sqm, deluxe rooms are exceptionally spacious, with a cool palette of marble, white and wood. Laze on your window seat or out on the terrace overlooking the desert. Wash off the day’s adventures under the rain shower or in the standalone tub.

roomTypes.name: One Bedroom Chott El Jerid View Villa
roomTypes.description: Your villa is ideal for hiding away, with spacious living adorned by modern Berber ceramics, fabrics, lanterns and wood carvings. Take breakfast out on the terrace in the cool morning air. Soak in the sunken tub with views of the desert framed by a floor-to-ceiling window.

roomTypes.name: Deluxe Garden View Suite
roomTypes.description: Our Deluxe Garden View Suites are luxurious havens of serenity offering soothing views of verdant palms. Contemplate natural beauty through oversized windows. Unwind in total comfort with pampering amenities and contemporary, locally inspired decor. Treat yourself to a revitalising bath in the soaking tub of your marble bathroom. Spend lazy days sprawled on the private terrace daybed, or savouring refined delicacies from the in-room dining service.

roomTypes.name: One Bedroom Anantara Pool Villa
roomTypes.description: Positioned at the edge of the resort overlooking nothing but desert, wake up to the sound of silence and spectacular sunrises. Pool villas offer spacious living both inside and out – spend days basking by the pool and nights dining under the stars.

roomTypes.name: Two Bedroom Anantara Family Pool Villa
roomTypes.description: Set out in the desert, your palatial hideaway consists of two ensuite bedrooms opening onto a central living room. Beyond, the terrace invites dining al fresco, served by your Villa Host. Spend the day lazing by the pool, before wandering into the sunset.
